== Chef Retrieve Node
Retrieves a information about a node in Chef within an organization.

=== Parameters
[Node Name]
  Name of node you wish to retrieve information about.

=== Sample Configuration
Node Name:        test-node

=== Results
[Node JSON]
  A JSON representation of the inputted node without with automatic attributes

=== Detailed Description
This handler retrieves a form.
  With the use of this handler, the you can retrieve the
  information about a node in Chef within an organization.
  This information will return in JSON format.
